                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Schuyler</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bangkok, Siam</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-08-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 10, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(With reference to the boycott of American goods, Chargé Schuyler reports that
                    3,000 Bangkok Chinese at a meeting held here have telegraphed to their agents at
                    Singapore and Hongkong not to ship any more American goods to Siam.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
